quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  19,26,"√ëaamu e …ìenndu…óe, yaraa ndiyam …óam, weltinir wonkii kin sanfaajo(cukulel) maa on wata a suno, si a yi'ii go…ó…óo e yim…ìe …ìen o lanndimaa kumpital fii sanfaajo on wi'an mo: "Min dey mi wa…ó…óinii e wonkii am fii Joomi am de∆¥∆¥ere gaayi haala, hannde mi yewtidataa gooto e yim…ìe …ìen."
  19,27,"Mariyama ardi e …ìi…ó…óo makko on ka yim…ìe makko …ìen himo tammbii mo, yim…ìe makko …ìen wi'ani mo e hoore a√±ugol: "Ko an yo Mariya, gom…óii a addii fiyaake maw…óo fefindaa…óo, nokku ka ardu…óaa e …ìi…ó…óo ko aldaa e baaba"."
  19,28,"Ko an yo nanndo Haaruuna ka dewal (on ko gorko mo∆¥∆¥o) baaba maa…óa wonaali jeenoowo, neene maa…óa kadi wonaali jeenoowo, an ko a iwdi suudu laa…ìundu anndiraandu mo∆¥∆¥ugol, ko honno addirtaa …ìi…ó…óo mo alaa baaba."
  19,29,"O sappii …ìi…ó…óo makko on Iisaa (yo o his) tawi himo ka wooforndu, yim…ìe [Mariyama] …ìen wi'ani mo hi…ìa haawoo: "Ko honno men yewtirta e boobo woofaa…óo?!""
  19,30,"Iisaa (yo o his) maaki: "Min dey ko mi jeyaa…óo Alla, O Okkii lam Linnjiila, O Wa…ói lam Annabaajo immorde e Annabaa…ìe Makko."
  19,31,"O Wa…ói lam heewu…óo nafa wonannde jeyaa…ìe …ìen nokku kala ka mi laatii, O Yamiri lam tottugol Julde nden e Jonnugol Jakka on juudde ngurndam am."
  19,32,"O Wa…ói lam …óiggan…óo Yumma am, O Wa…óaali lam mawnintinanii…óo doftagol Joomi am, wanaa mi yeddoowo Mo."
  19,33,"Hoolaare e [bone] Seytaane e walloo…ìe mo …ìen wonii e am √±alnde mi jibinanoo e √±alnde mi maayata e √ëalnde mi immintintee ko mi wuuru…óo √ëalnde Darngal, Seytaane foppaaki lam e nder …óii nokkuuli tati wul…óin…ói(njeewdi.)"
  19,34,"On siforaa…óo …óin sifaaji ko kanko woni Iisaa ge…óal Mariyama, kaa haala …óoo ko …óum woni konngol Goongawol ngol e mu'un, wanaa ko majju…ìe …ìen wi'ata kon, …ìen sikkitotoo…ìe e fiyaake makko …ìe luutondira."
  19,35,"Haananaa Alla nde O jogitotoo …ìi…ó…óo, O Laa…ìii gaayi …óum O Senike, si O faandike huunde, pellet, yonay Mo Senayee wonanii Mo nde O Daalanta nden huunde: "Wonu", nde wona feere alaa, ko nii O woniri Kanko ko O Senii…óo e gaayi …ìi…ó…óo."
  19,36,"Pellet, Alla Senayee wonanii Mo ko Kanko woni Joomi am, ko Kanko kadi woni Joomi mo'on, la…ì…ìinanee Mo Dewal ngal Kanko Tun, …óum ko mi ja≈ãtanii on ko …óum woni Laawol Focciingol ngol yottinayngol e Welayee Alla."
  19,37,"luutrii luutru…ìe …ìen fii fiyaake Iisaa (yo o his) …ìe luutondiri …ìe wonti feddeeji sertu…ói e hakkunde yim…ìe makko, yoga ma…ì…ìe gom…óini …ìe wi'i: "Ko o Nulaa…óo" wo…ó…ìe goo yeddi mo wano Alyahuuda en, wano fedde goo yeewiri non e fii makko wo…ó…ìe ma…ì…ìe wi'i: "Ko Kanko woni Alla". Wo…ó…ìe goo kadi wi'i: "Ko o …ìi…ó…óo Alla". Alla Toowii gaayi …óum, bone wonanii …ìen luutondir…ìe e fii fiyaake makko e taweede √ëalnde Darngal Mawngal sabu ko woni e maggal e seedafuyeeji e Hasboore e Lepte."
  19,38,"Kaawee ko nanirta wa ma…ì…ìe nden √±alnde kaawee ko yi'irta wa ma…ì…ìe, …ìe nanii fewndo nan…óe nafataa …ìe, …ìe yi'ii fewndo gii…óe nafataa …ìe, kono too√±oo…ìe …ìen ka ngurndan aduna hi…ìe e nder majjere …ìanngunde gaayi Laawol Focciingol ngol, …ìe alaa heblanaade Laakara on haa o ara e ma…ì…ìe e juhayee hara kam…ìe hi…ìe e hoore too√±e ma…ì…ìe …óen."